meta {
  name: 5. Resolve — default link (bare scan)
  type: http
  seq: 5
}

get {
  url: {{dl-url}}/01/{{gtin}}
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  What a plain QR scan does: GET /01/{gtin} with no linkType returns the
  defaultLink as a 302 -> demo.epcis.cloud/01/{gtin} (the product page). Before
  the fix this looped back to the resolver ("too many redirects"); now it lands
  on the DDM. Toggle "Follow Redirects" off to show the raw 302 in the demo.
}
